      • FlagCompoundsEmpirical

        public static void FlagCompoundsEmpirical(CompoundList cpdlist,
                                          TargetList tgtlist,
                                          Integer tid_query,
                                          Integer cid_query)
        For drug-queries, targets must be flagged 1st. Target-query: Flag cpds active on target. Disease-query: Flag cpds active on targets linked to disease. Drug-query: After tgtlist has been flagged based on a drug-query, flag cpdlist based on empirical drug-target-compound links.
